## Components — 21 Available

### When to Use Which
- **Tile vs List**: Tile for selection cards with title+description; List for simple menu rows
- **Chip vs Badge**: Chip is interactive (filter, remove, toggle); Badge is static (status label)
- **Dropdown vs Radio**: Dropdown for 4+ options or space-constrained; Radio for 2-4 visible choices
- **Notification vs Dialog**: Notification for inline status banners; Dialog for blocking confirmations
- **Search vs Text Input**: Search has a leading search icon + auto-clear; Text Input for form fields

### Button
`udc-button-primary` / `udc-button-secondary` / `udc-button-ghost`
Variants: `data-size="sm"`, `data-leading-icon`, `data-trailing-icon`, `data-icon-only`, `data-btn-color="danger"`, `disabled`
```html
<button class="udc-button-primary">Save</button>
<button class="udc-button-secondary">Cancel</button>
<button class="udc-button-ghost" data-icon-only><span class="material-symbols-outlined">more_vert</span></button>
```

### Text Input
`udc-text-input` → `__label`, `__required`, `__field`, `__helper`, `__counter`, `__trailing-btn`
States: `data-state="error"`
```html
<div class="udc-text-input">
  <label class="udc-text-input__label">Email<span class="udc-text-input__required"></span></label>
  <div class="udc-text-input__field"><input type="email" placeholder="Enter email..." /></div>
  <div class="udc-text-input__helper"><span>Helper text</span><span class="udc-text-input__counter">0/100</span></div>
</div>
```

### Dropdown
`udc-dropdown` → `__label`, `__trigger`, `__value`, `__chevron`, `__list`, `__item`, `__helper`
States: `data-open="true"`, `data-state="error"`, `aria-disabled="true"`
```html
<div class="udc-dropdown">
  <label class="udc-dropdown__label">Property</label>
  <div class="udc-dropdown__trigger" tabindex="0" role="combobox" aria-expanded="false" aria-haspopup="listbox">
    <span class="udc-dropdown__value" data-placeholder>Select...</span>
    <span class="udc-dropdown__chevron"><span class="material-symbols-outlined">keyboard_arrow_down</span></span>
  </div>
  <div class="udc-dropdown__list" role="listbox">
    <div class="udc-dropdown__item" role="option">Option A</div>
  </div>
</div>
```

### Search
`udc-search` → `__field`, `__icon`, `__clear`
States: `data-state="error"`, `data-has-value="true"`
```html
<div class="udc-search">
  <div class="udc-search__field">
    <span class="udc-search__icon"><span class="material-symbols-outlined">search</span></span>
    <input type="search" placeholder="Search..." />
    <button class="udc-search__clear" aria-label="Clear"><span class="material-symbols-outlined">clear</span></button>
  </div>
</div>
```

### Data Table
`udc-data-table` + `udc-dt-check`, `udc-dt-sort`, `udc-dt-filter`, `udc-dt-action`, `udc-dt-align-right`, `udc-dt-align-center`, `udc-dt-prominent`
States: `data-striped="true"`, `data-highlight="error"`
```html
<div class="udc-data-table">
  <table>
    <thead><tr>
      <th class="udc-dt-check"><input type="checkbox" /></th>
      <th>Name <span class="udc-dt-sort" data-dir="asc"></span></th>
      <th>Status</th>
      <th class="udc-dt-align-right">Amount</th>
      <th class="udc-dt-action"></th>
    </tr></thead>
    <tbody><tr>
      <td class="udc-dt-check"><input type="checkbox" /></td>
      <td>Brian Smith</td>
      <td><span class="udc-badge" data-variant="success">Active</span></td>
      <td class="udc-dt-align-right">$1,200</td>
      <td class="udc-dt-action"><button class="udc-button-ghost" data-icon-only><span class="material-symbols-outlined">more_vert</span></button></td>
    </tr></tbody>
  </table>
</div>
```

