</div>
```

## Keyboard Patterns for React/Vue

Since React/Vue don't use `uds.js`, implement these keyboard behaviors:

- **Dropdown**: ArrowUp/Down to navigate items, Enter/Space to select, Escape to close
- **Dialog**: Escape to close, Tab cycles within dialog (focus trap), auto-focus first element on open
- **Tabs**: ArrowLeft/Right between tabs, Home/End for first/last
- **List**: ArrowUp/Down to navigate, Enter/Space to select
- **Tile**: Enter/Space to toggle selection
- **Data Table sort**: Enter/Space on header to cycle sort direction

## Error & Validation Patterns

- Validate on **blur** (not every keystroke)
- Set `data-state="error"` on the `udc-text-input` or `udc-dropdown` wrapper
- Replace helper text with the error message
- Clear error on next input event
- For form-level errors, show `<div class="udc-notification" data-variant="error">...</div>`

## Common Icons

Navigation: `space_dashboard`, `book`, `contact_phone`, `home_work`, `monetization_on`, `settings`, `account_circle`, `notifications`
Actions: `add`, `edit`, `delete`, `close`, `search`, `clear`, `download`, `more_vert`, `chevron_right`, `keyboard_arrow_down`
Status: `info`, `check_circle`, `error_outline`, `warning_amber`
Content: `apartment`, `home`, `mail`, `phone`, `calendar_today`

## Do's and Don'ts

```
DO:    var(--uds-color-text-primary)           DON'T: #171717
DO:    var(--uds-color-surface-main)           DON'T: #fafafa
DO:    var(--uds-space-200)                    DON'T: 16px
DO:    var(--uds-font-family)                  DON'T: 'Inter', sans-serif
DO:    var(--uds-border-radius-input)          DON'T: 8px
DO:    var(--uds-shadow-depth-300)             DON'T: 0 4px 12px rgba(0,0,0,0.08)
DO:    var(--uds-color-text-interactive)       DON'T: var(--uds-primitive-color-blue-60-M)
```

### React:
- `className` not `class`, `htmlFor` not `for`, `tabIndex` not `tabindex`
- `useState` for ALL interactive state, controlled inputs with `value` + `onChange`
- NEVER: `dangerouslySetInnerHTML`, `uds.js`, uncontrolled inputs

### Vue:
- `<script setup>` + Composition API, `ref()` for state, `v-model` for inputs
- NEVER: `v-html`, Options API, `uds.js`

### Custom CSS (non-UDS layouts):
Use UDS tokens for ALL values. Example:
```css
.my-hero {
  background: var(--uds-color-surface-subtle);
  padding: var(--uds-space-500) var(--uds-space-300);
  border-radius: var(--uds-border-radius-container-md);
  font-family: var(--uds-font-family);
}
.my-hero h1 {
  font-size: var(--uds-font-size-5xl);
  font-weight: var(--uds-font-weight-bold);
  color: var(--uds-color-text-primary);
  margin-bottom: var(--uds-space-200);
}
```

## Project Boilerplate

### React (Vite)
```jsx
// main.jsx
import React from 'react';
import ReactDOM from 'react-dom/client';
import 'uds-core/uds.css';
import App from './App.jsx';
ReactDOM.createRoot(document.getElementById('root')).render(<App />);
```

